212-570-3750</p>
<p><strong>By Mail:</strong><br />
The Metropolitan Museum of Art<br />
Event Box Office<br />
1000 Fifth Avenue<br />
New York, New York 10028-0198<br />
United States of America</p>
<p><strong>In Person:</strong><br />
If you are placing a ticket order in person at the Museum, you may indicate your preference to Museum staff when purchasing your tickets.</p>
<p>We may also share your personal information with third-party service marketing partners to personalize your shopping experience on our and other websites. For details, see <a href="#ThirdPartyServiceProviders">Third-Party Service Providers</a>.</p>
